{"tid":1800051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）懷疑波台鏝區手足「花插皇后庭」被失蹤","createTime":"2019-12-27T12:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T17:27:29.000Z","uid":47268,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70b586a3059d18c84e28205f7e1a2def6d4c9b6f","tid":1800051,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"首先大家如果唔係鏝狗可能唔係好識呢個人<br />\n呢條友喺鏝區不嬲都係比較搶口嗰群黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WE18vd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WE18vd.png&h=fb7a8f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見佢一直都係開緊反猁po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但喺反送中運動開始咗之後<br />\n花ching就一直都活躍於cctai<br />\n開咗好多行動po<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FJRMhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FJRMhV.png&h=d5fb27dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁呢件事都係正常既<br />\n反送中運動開始咗之後有唔少波台手足都會開始上cctai<br />\n例如已經上到回曬塘既港父<br />\n<br />\n但問題黎啦<br />\n自從8月中開始，花ching就冇出過po<br />\n更加冇喺鏝區蒲頭<br />\n之後我覺得唔對路就叫埋水塘去搵佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBgzJ6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBgzJ6v.png&h=532cd91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺之後我地都冇再理呢件事<br />\n<br />\n但喺今日，花插皇后庭突然上水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFuEVdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFuEVdQ.png&h=468d2803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲喺到借啲意講話今年冇心情睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我極度懷疑花ching真佢已經作為勇武比黑警收咗皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想用佢個ac帶風向<br />\n但咁啱又有兩隻鏝狗搵緊佢<br />\n就上水扮撚曬野話冇心情睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我9up的，但如果比我估中咗，希望警察叔叔唔好搞鳩我，我唔想成為第二個柚木巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b248449236f1f76c163450403af4aac9e413f717","tid":1800051,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4936f28ac624e04f898c907858401e589e4ac7d6","tid":1800051,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d19929dde7a0326ce577a9ae43e50f4ff93a0f2c","tid":1800051,"uid":4308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n樓主黑警黎"},{"pid":"ef6cb82dd4fba28ff22a2c99dc475f02d186a86b","tid":1800051,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"大事大非唔好25ok?"},{"pid":"a4323a46b17c4cced4b5f94361ce4def8c6d5a54","tid":1800051,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"你地有無人識佢真人？"},{"pid":"b619706563658c8b9d8e12b8cf1dc0090a0b89c1","tid":1800051,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc368ed48869374ec9ec54c4c372304838341de","tid":1800051,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19929dde7a0326ce577a9ae43e50f4ff93a0f2c","tid":1800051,"uid":4308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n樓主黑警黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c450a83eb0577631a1640613763078fe5348de","tid":1800051,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6cb82dd4fba28ff22a2c99dc475f02d186a86b","tid":1800051,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"大事大非唔好25ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"Yes sir"},{"pid":"2b9408bf83b3a6e9963948bb76fef0e564015ae7","tid":1800051,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":